A minimalistic chatbot for slack

I used my keys, but if anyone is downloading this,
Please create a bot_info.py in this folder 
with 3 variables: 
VALET_SLACK_TOKEN = xxxxxx
VALET_SLACK_NAME = 'valet'
VALET_SLACK_ID = xxxxx


References:
----------
https://medium.com/@nidhog/how-to-make-a-chatbot-on-slack-with-python-82015517f19c
https://github.com/gunthercox/ChatterBot

